[3] USA: spending bill includes Ebola response funding
Date: Fri 19 Dec 2014
Source: Africare [edited]
http://www.africare.org/ebola-outbreak-update-week-december-14-2014


On 16 Dec 2014, US President Barack Obama signed an omnibus spending bill. The bill allocated USD 5.4 billion to fight Ebola in the United States and abroad, with USD 2.5 billion specifically appropriated to respond to the Ebola outbreak in West Africa.

